  "name": "Courage and Destiny",
  "description": "A single act of courage can rewrite a lifetime. George's punch transforms him from victim to hero. The theme mirrors Marty's own arc: he is told never to be called 'chicken,' and his journey in 1955 is ultimately about finding the nerve to act.",
